  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/b85c226e6f734d5c06aa18a17922e0c9.avif?t=1764796363\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Food Factory</strong> is a game where players produce food using various machines, starting from gathering raw ingredients. Buy land for your factory, build efficient production lines, expand your operations, gather resources, and explore new areas. Drive over 20 different vehicles and trailers, including harvesters, forklifts, trucks, pickups, and vans. Export your finished products or deliver them to local sellers. Take on side missions to earn extra money — and even furnish your home or factory to make it your own. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/3cddae9232a9173b7f24dad5f37375a7.avif?t=1764796363\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Grow several types of different plants.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/d6acdbf333b31f02347e06cf07c9b799.poster.avif?t=1764796363\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/d6acdbf333b31f02347e06cf07c9b799.webm?t=1764796363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/d6acdbf333b31f02347e06cf07c9b799.mp4?t=1764796363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/e3fa2840b2a69484f668a9ec557eda08.avif?t=1764796363\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Build your factory!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/9672668c4c84956b4437e307a1878eaa.poster.avif?t=1764796363\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/9672668c4c84956b4437e307a1878eaa.webm?t=1764796363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/9672668c4c84956b4437e307a1878eaa.mp4?t=1764796363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/2bf4d9c876e6de89ba5e4a8206fd4b7a.poster.avif?t=1764796363\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/2bf4d9c876e6de89ba5e4a8206fd4b7a.webm?t=1764796363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/2bf4d9c876e6de89ba5e4a8206fd4b7a.mp4?t=1764796363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/2c31459c51c7fcda0221b16c5caaa5cf.avif?t=1764796363\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Try different vehicles to make your factory life easier!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/878942361ad805c73f4ae8b574af3fbc.poster.avif?t=1764796363\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/878942361ad805c73f4ae8b574af3fbc.webm?t=1764796363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/878942361ad805c73f4ae8b574af3fbc.mp4?t=1764796363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/b85c226e6f734d5c06aa18a17922e0c9.avif?t=1764796363\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Food Factory</strong> is a game where players produce food using various machines, starting from gathering raw ingredients. Buy land for your factory, build efficient production lines, expand your operations, gather resources, and explore new areas. Drive over 20 different vehicles and trailers, including harvesters, forklifts, trucks, pickups, and vans. Export your finished products or deliver them to local sellers. Take on side missions to earn extra money — and even furnish your home or factory to make it your own. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/3cddae9232a9173b7f24dad5f37375a7.avif?t=1764796363\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Grow several types of different plants.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/d6acdbf333b31f02347e06cf07c9b799.poster.avif?t=1764796363\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/d6acdbf333b31f02347e06cf07c9b799.webm?t=1764796363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019920/extras/d6acdbf333b31f02347e06cf07c9b799.mp4?t=1764796363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"